name: Travel Tags - Set A
description:
A set of six travel tags for scrapbooking, paper projects (or print them out as stickers!). Each tag is roughly 3 inches high and varies in width. Included in the download are individual .PNG files and one PDF. 

Itinerary:
Tokyo
San Francisco
Paris
Amsterdam
London
New York

A collection of my favorite places!
